n/wiki/Migration#migrating-to-162\r\n\r\nI see a warning about this when running the dsl jobs:\r\n\r\n* https://build.osrfoundation.org/job/_dsl_ignition/394/console\r\n\r\n~~~\r\nProcessing DSL script ignition.dsl\r\nWarning: (OSRFLinuxBuildPkgBase.groovy, line 33) postBuildScripts is deprecated\r\n~~~", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The Jenkins Post-build script plugin has <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://jenkins.io/security/advisory/2017-04-10/#post-build-script-plugin\" rel=\"nofollow\">security problems</a> and is deprecated:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jenkinsci/job-dsl-plugin/wiki/Migration#migrating-to-162\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://github.com/jenkinsci/job-dsl-plugin/wiki/Migration#migrating-to-162</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>I see a warning about this when running the dsl jobs:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://build.osrfoundation.org/job/_dsl_ignition/394/console\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://build.osrfoundation.org/job/_dsl_ignition/394/console</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>Processing DSL script ignition.dsl\nWarning: (OSRFLinuxBuildPkgBase.groovy, line 33) postBuildScripts is deprecated\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2017-09-29T16:55:32.162810+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2017-11-17T18:42:10.965492+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 118}